<td valign="top">
<p><strong>Vision </strong></p><p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><strong><font size="2">to              be the prominent body of professional information security practitioners, and              utilize our expertise and knowledge to help bring prosperity              to the society in the Information Age</font></strong></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Mission</strong> </p><ul><li><strong><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#666666">to                  facilitate knowledge and information sharing among the PISA members                  </font></strong></li><li><strong><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#666666">                  to promote the highest quality of technical and ethical standards                  to the information security profession,</font></strong></li><li><strong><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#666666">                  to promote best-practices in information security control,</font></strong></li><li><strong><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#666666">                  to promote security awareness to the IT industry and general public                  in Hong Kong,</font></strong></li><li><strong><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#666666">to                  be the de facto representative body of local information security                  professionals</font></strong></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>

</table>
